158
00:11:28,604 --> 00:11:30,106
Did you come to my funeral?

159
00:11:30,231 --> 00:11:31,982
This is my birthday party.

160
00:11:32,066 --> 00:11:33,317
Birthday.

161
00:11:34,318 --> 00:11:37,530
