806
00:58:16,201 --> 00:58:17,577
-Whatever.
-You little...

807
00:58:20,914 --> 00:58:21,956
What?

808
00:58:23,833 --> 00:58:24,792
That brat...

809
00:58:24,876 --> 00:58:25,835
Next news.

