for the murder of Yang Jin-wu.

828
00:59:30,149 --> 00:59:32,110
You have the right to a lawyer

829
00:59:32,610 --> 00:59:34,445
and to resist an unlawful apprehension.

830
00:59:34,946 --> 00:59:36,155
If you have anything to say...

