00:59:37,865 --> 00:59:41,286
He could be
another wrongly accused suspect like me.

832
00:59:43,663 --> 00:59:46,249
He's our first client.

833
01:00:08,479 --> 01:00:11,107
This is the definition
of the word, "beginning."

